{"tid":417972,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新貓舊貓相處 求指教","createTime":"2017-09-29T07:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T12:47:37.000Z","uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f524ed47f87a6ab615a92d68b8dd0a6284c69d3a","tid":417972,"uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"我屋企本身有隻貓 依家五個月大左右 仔 未結紮啦因為先得五個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴日接咗隻新貓返嚟 得一個半月大 女 <br />\n兩隻都係英短 舊貓性格親人 都唔算惡的 <br />\n之後琴日兩隻貓一見面都冇哈氣 互相觀察咁啦<br />\n舊貓都有新隻手入個籠打下新貓 冇伸爪<br />\n新貓偶爾都會新隻手出嚟 兩隻貓互相打下咁 冇伸爪但有用力的 都有想咬下對方(但咬唔到因為隔住個籠）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽到舊貓都有發出啲震音 上網睇係話表示friendly (?)<br />\n之後試過放隻新貓仔出來一陣 諗住佢哋相處應該都OK<br />\n但點知舊貓走上去咬 但又唔係咬後頸 係咬後頸同耳仔嘅中間位 都有咬個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲想咬住佢咁拖走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新貓都應該痛 所以有大聲喵 所以我就放返佢入籠<br />\n<br />\n我想問究竟佢哋咬咬下咁係玩定係真係有敵意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為初初見都OK 又冇哈氣 打都冇伸爪 但係一放出來又咬又拖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪我太心急 應該點做？佢地究竟係玩定點架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求各位巴絲指教一下我呢個養貓新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221034bbdcda66a38dafd39fa4f0f51b57b62f58","tid":417972,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"正常，佢地要打過先會知邊個係大佬"},{"pid":"350794cb7c0566b0e7ea4344b38187769bfdd9d6","tid":417972,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03d65c756eea3cb847c6027f8aa6cf53b2ce465b","tid":417972,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"舊貓未絕育前小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29830b207905c26ed00a1bb51545514bb44b7054","tid":417972,"uid":27396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"你打佢地先 等佢地知道邊個先係真正既大佬"},{"pid":"6383e191310734fae5fc0931e28dd10aa68f6f85","tid":417972,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你打佢地先 等佢地知道邊個先係真正既大佬</blockquote><br />\n兩隻貓有左共同敵人就唔會鬼打鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5446459ee44a21a1cb05349aa7bc597a1d1178d","tid":417972,"uid":126809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"本身養開隻英短 之後再養多隻美短 而家隻美短已經養咗半年到 但每次隻英短見到隻美短都勁有敵意 打到啲毛甩撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e42700a6d6fca326e3a1a659da1631fe063faae","tid":417972,"uid":126629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"養咗七年，兩隻依然世仇咁"},{"pid":"73365fe8d5752de4078cd3464854584c4532f6d8","tid":417972,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊貓未絕育前小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於可以做貓公了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd646caf31b1a37e0eaa8082cfdb828b698b7a00","tid":417972,"uid":115778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:49:33.000Z","msg":"看屋企兩隻嗰陣都係噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇到隻新貓到而家唔係肚餓都會喱埋唔出嚟"},{"pid":"32c6602c37087ddbf75e1ee957c6620c605dfb73","tid":417972,"uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身養開隻英短 之後再養多隻美短 而家隻美短已經養咗半年到 但每次隻英短見到隻美短都勁有敵意 打到啲毛甩撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明佢地又冇哈氣喎"},{"pid":"1fcb63e259e449cb937edefd88c8a95a2f5207d5","tid":417972,"uid":90969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"比多啲關愛舊貓，等佢唔好覺得自己失寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20947ce5a504179f5ef14a09ca36c0e1328998cb","tid":417972,"uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比多啲關愛舊貓，等佢唔好覺得自己失寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經特登唔係好理新貓"},{"pid":"be0a74e25928a9da61083e611652c463e06c8b1f","tid":417972,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"好明顯太心急 至少過多一星期先比佢地正式見面<br />\n等舊貓適應咗先 之後如果細貓打大貓 睇下大貓夠唔夠打先<br />\n唔夠你要出聲幫大貓 跟住拍下細貓屎忽同埋鬧細貓<br />\n但真係係大貓唔夠打嘅情況下先出手幫<br />\n呢段時間盡量錫大貓多啲<br />\n如果佢地打架唔係去到太過份其實由佢地<br />\n等佢地知道邊個大邊個細"},{"pid":"8aaa4f26b78b788c53c1cdbe1dba9079a49d04b8","tid":417972,"uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:04:09.000Z","msg":"[member] testing [member]"},{"pid":"3d1bf0a91d0b235826af060a99f25a7898e15a71","tid":417972,"uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[member] testing [member]</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016ad87ed0900a9a0237670beba1631964839e4f","tid":417972,"uid":141561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[member] testing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n[member] testing </blockquote><br />\n[member] testing"},{"pid":"2e674cc71e7b180e7d8aedcc91e836ef2409d5c1","tid":417972,"u